### Get All Orders (paginated)
GET http://localhost/orders?page=1&limit=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Single Order by ID
GET http://localhost/orders/3
Accept: application/json

###

### Create New Order
POST http://localhost/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample Order",
  "amount_in_stock": 199,
  "price": 99.99,
  "status": "PENDING"
}

###

### Update Existing Order
PUT http://localhost/orders/6
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Order Name",
  "amount_in_stock": 123,
  "price": 79.95,
  "status": "SHIPPED"
}

###

### Delete Order
DELETE http://localhost/orders/6
Accept: application/json
